To identify the muscle synergies, we applied a non-negative matrix factorization (NMF) to the pre-processed EMG. In the NMF algorithm, the EMG was modeled as a synergy matrix (W) multiplied by the corresponding activation profile matrix (C):1\documentclass[12pt]{minimal}
				\usepackage{amsmath}
				\usepackage{wasysym} 
				\usepackage{amsfonts} 
				\usepackage{amssymb} 
				\usepackage{amsbsy}
