				\begin{document}$${\text{Th}}_{{{\text{CoA}}}} = \frac{1}{\sqrt 8 } = 0.35$$\end{document}ThCoA=18=0.35). ThCoA was determined based on the normalized weight of each muscle within a synergy if all eight muscles were equally activated. Using the selected m1base and m2base, we quantified the disparity index (DI) of a muscle pair at the baseline (DIbase) as:3\documentclass[12pt]{minimal}
